OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChildren used as 'guinea   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpigs' in clinical trials   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The true scale of the number of medical
OL,6, trials using infected blood products on
OL,7, children in the 1970s and 80s has been 
OL,8, revealed by documents seen by BBC News.
OL,10,FThey reveal a secret world of unsafe   
OL,11,Fclinical testing involving children in 
OL,12,Fthe UK, as doctors placed research     
OL,13,Fgoals ahead of patients' needs.        
OL,15,FThey continued for more than 15 years, 
OL,16,Finvolved hundreds of people, and       
OL,17,Finfected most with hepatitis C and HIV.
OL,19,FOne surviving patient told the BBC he  
OL,20,Fwas treated like a "guinea pig".       
